idea-plugin.description:
This plugin will easily build a  catalog(SUMMARY.md) from three kinds of document source
such as swagger, lark(alibaba), database(only support mysql) by entering just a few information.
The plugin provide a pre-config in which you can set the token for lark document ,
set sql connection for database document, that can make building much more easily;
visit   https://yuque.antfin-inc.com/2018_tprojects/p-doc   to learn more about the plugin;

